                    <h2 class="headings">&#126; History &#126;</h2>
                    <p class="content">The Jaipuria Group's history in education began in 1945 with the establishment of
                        Seth Anandram
                        Jaipuria Commerce College in Kolkata. The college is still operational today and has around
                        7,000
                        students.The group's history in K-12 education began in 1974 with the establishment of Seth
                        Anandram
                        Jaipuria School in Kanpur. </p>
                </div>

